OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy start
OL,6,Fto the evening with any isolated
OL,7,Fshowers dying out and clear intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fspells in the west, cloudier in east
OL,10,Fwith some patchy light rain returning.
OL,11,FBreezy near the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA mostly cloudy start with
OL,14,Fsome patchy light rain, but some sunny
OL,15,Fintervals on west coast and then sunny
OL,16,Fspells developing more widely in the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Breezy on west coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
